# Key Findings — VeriSimply CCTV Analysis

## Finding 1: Funnel Drop-off
- Clear drop-off point identified between Quote Given and Sale Closed
- This stage had lowest conversion — targeted for improvement

## Finding 2: Top Packages
- Top 3 CCTV packages drove majority of total revenue
- Lower-tier packages had higher inquiry volume but lower conversion

## Finding 3: Peak Demand Periods
- Specific months showed 2-3x higher inquiry volume
- Product-specific peaks identified — different packages peak at different times

## Business Decisions Made
1. Inventory aligned to peak demand periods
2. Marketing spend redirected to high-conversion product types
3. Management dashboard replaced manual monthly reporting

## PM Translation
- Funnel analysis = identifying where users drop off in a product flow
- Peak period = feature rollout timing
- Dashboard = self-service metrics for non-technical stakeholders
